Narration, Topshe - Somak

Deeananath Lahiri - Ambarish Bhattacharya
Sidhujyatha  - Sukomal Ghosh.
Prabir Lahiri – Chayan Roy.

Feluda theme – Satyajit Ray

Introduction, Direction - Agni
